$$ see: hide, inventory, smuggler, unconceal
 --=== Conceal ===--  (Smuggler Guild Command)

 Usage: conceal [item | all]

 Smugglers can conceal items in their inventory.  Some items cannot be concealed, such as wielded weapons or worn armor.  This ability is based on your Hiding skill.

 Everyone can type 'conceal' to see if they are concealing any items, as well as 'unconceal'.